{"tid":1728494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱行動毋須上報 官媒速刪報道","createTime":"2019-11-17T01:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:13:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d65d8e4c5281426e1a8a29c124f81b74d8111bd5","tid":1728494,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:57:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191117/QRZKXDVUSDXRZ6UZB3HPAI7QYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191117%2FQRZKXDVUSDXRZ6UZB3HPAI7QYU%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=4b253f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191117%2FQRZKXDVUSDXRZ6UZB3HPAI7QYU%2F&h=6acd48ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191117/QRZKXDVUSDXRZ6UZB3HPAI7QYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n稱行動毋須上報 官媒速刪報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191117/large/1573921638_733d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573921638_733d.jpg&h=f7416445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國共和黨俞懷松昨在Twitter發帖，指駐軍行動難騙任何人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港社會與暴政抗爭幾個月來，首次有解放軍步出軍營「自發清障」，引起各方揣測。北京官媒《環球時報》、《人民日報》網站均第一時間報道有關消息，其中《環時》引述「權威人士」稱，駐港軍人出營活動僅需本單位批准，叫外界「毋須過度解讀」，不過兩者的網上報道出街不久即被消失。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》引「權威人士」指，駐港官兵出軍營僅需本單位批准，並不需要上升到更高層面，且此次官兵沒穿制服，又是周六休息時間，表明駐港部隊刻意降低身份敏感性。<br />\n<br />\n該人士續指，外界毋須過度解讀官兵出營，更不能以此來判斷駐港部有進一步動作。《環時》總編輯胡錫進亦在晚上7時發帖稱，解放軍行動限於營區周邊，且那些路障也阻礙駐港部隊車輛進出，不認為駐港部隊藉這次行動，對外傳遞所謂政治信號，不過有關文字很快被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俞懷松：騙不了任何人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：虎頭標識 特戰營疑至少有八連<br />\n<br />\n至於《人民日報》海外版網站也以「暖心！駐港解放軍協助香港市民清理路障」為題，引述香港有關駐港部隊出軍營清路障的報道，不過報道也很快被消失。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一直關注香港抗爭的美國共和黨海外事務組織副主席俞懷松（Solomon Yue）亦發帖評論事件，形容此舉是駐港解放軍「魅力攻勢」，但「騙不了任何人」，又指駐軍行動「不應以抵觸基本法為代價」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者沈燕媚"},{"pid":"c2010dbf30e05e39c2769c918b0ae733dd11ba96","tid":1728494,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"（緊急要人）再唔出嚟幫手下星期黎明行動成效一定會大減<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728462</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f68bcf12f5ea51726f62b8b21d38368c27ac3af","tid":1728494,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gn4citE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGn4citE.jpg&h=ba06b3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8sEHcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8sEHcf.jpg&h=b80c15d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntFV0Aq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntFV0Aq.png&h=9b9d7178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcdc69af09bfcda576dc8ca1f765c13452ce1eb4","tid":1728494,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99668faac521704d152efcfcf454194d47048f12","tid":1728494,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:27:56.000Z","msg":"政府打緊公關戰同輿論戰，口誅筆伐黎解散呢場運動，手足知唔知我地下一步要點做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75d6cb3116752ffe8da35bf872e2db0b52ac6593","tid":1728494,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"士兵行動無需上報？咁仲有軍紀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728812e98f94f0c68542a2d426bcde2ce8d8c5df","tid":1728494,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"支那人做野真係好柒好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />